tment portfolio and almost all of the loans for which we retain the obligation to service as a result of our correspondent lending operations pennymac mortgage investment trust has elected to be taxed as a real estate investment trust reit for us federal income tax purposes the companys stock trades on the new york stock exchange under the ticker symbol pmt  annual report click here to view the presentations documents news releasesdatetitlepennymac mortgage investment trust prices public offering of  percent series b fixedtofloating rate cumulative redeemable preferred sharespennymac mortgage investment trust declares second quarter  dividendpennymac mortgage investment trust announces preferred share dividendpennymac mortgage investment trust reports first quarter  resultspennymac mortgage investment trust announces date for release of first quarter  resultspennymac mortgage investment trust announces date for  annual meeting of shareholderspennymac mortgage investment trust declares first quarter  dividendpennymac mortgage investment trust prices public offering of  percent series a fixedtofloating rate cumulative redeemable preferred sharespennymac mortgage investment trust reports fourth quarter and fullyear  resultspennymac mortgage investment trust announces date for release of fourth quarter  and fullyear  resultsnews releasespennymac mortgage investment trust prices public offering of  percent series b fixedtofloating rate cumulative redeemable preferred sharespennymac mortgage investment trust declares second quarter  dividendpennymac mortgage investment trust announces preferred share dividendpennymac mortgage investment trust reports first quarter  resultspennymac mortgage investment trust announces date for release of first quarter  resultspennymac mortgage investment trust announces date for  annual meeting of shareholderspennymac mortgage investment trust declares first quarter  dividendpennymac mortgage investment trust prices public offering of  perc